;W[ps]LB[rs:1][sp:2][ps:3][qr:A]C[Dia.3 Correct / The placement  attack

White 1 is the correct followup to the placement attack.  Even if Black tries 2 it doesn't work for him because White can dansu at 3 and Black cannot connect at A because he doesn't have enough liberties.
\lang1042\f1\fs18

